# Authbox LDAP Schema
#
# This file is applied on first boot after the base DN and OUs are created.
# Edit before first boot to add custom attributes or objectClasses.
# The base DN (dc=example,dc=com) is replaced with LDAP_BASE_DN at load time.
#
# Core schemas (core, cosine, inetorgperson, nis) are loaded by slapd bootstrap.
# Base DN, OUs, and role groups are created by the Go app.
#
# Add custom entries below if needed. Leave empty for default setup.
